<Layout title="Audit Mobile Forensique | D&eacute;tecter une compromission sur Android et iOS — Gigarun La Réunion" description="Guide complet d">
<div style="background:#07001C;padding-top:8rem;padding-bottom:2rem;">
  <div style="max-width:56rem;margin:0 auto;padding:0 1.5rem;text-align:center;">
    <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3" style="justify-content:center;">
      <a href="/blog" class="text-[#9B99AA] hover:text-[#7C3AED] text-sm transition-colors">← Blog &amp; Guides</a>
    </div>
    <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-2" style="justify-content:center;">
      <span class="bg-[#110833] border border-[rgba(124,58,237,0.3)] text-[#7C3AED] text-[11px] font-medium px-3 py-1 rounded-full">Guide pratique · Cybersécurité</span>
    </div>
    <h1 class="font-syne font-extrabold text-[#F1F0F7] leading-tight text-center" style="font-size:clamp(24px,3.5vw,40px);text-align:center;">Audit Mobile Forensique | D&eacute;tecter une compromission sur Android et iOS</h1>
    <p class="text-\[#9B99AA\] text-sm mt-2 mb-0" style="text-align:center;">Guide complet d</p>
  </div>
